root: ^Hey there! Welcome to our humble farm.
^Yeah, it really doesn't look like much now, does it?
^I swear, we're usually bustling with crops, but...
^Well, without the bees to pollinate everything, we've not been having much luck recently. At least the chickens didn't up and fly off too!
^Also, don't mind my husband, he's very stressed out just now. I am too of course, but lets just say we're opposites when it comes to working under pressure.
